* Antony E. Alcock (2003). ''The History of the South Tyrol Question''. London: Michael Joseph. 535 pp.
* [[Rolf_Steininger|Rolf Steininger]] (2003). ''South Tyrol: A Minority Conflict of the Twentieth Century''. New Brunswick, New Jersey: Transaction Publishers. {{ISBN|978-0-7658-0800-4}}
* Georg Grote (2012). ''The South Tyrol Question 1866–2010. From National Rage to Regional State''. Oxford: [[Peter_Lang|Peter Lang]]. {{ISBN|978-3-03911-336-1}}
* Georg Grote, Hannes Obermair (2017). ''A Land on the Threshold. South Tyrolean Transformations, 1915–2015.'' Oxford/Bern/New York: Peter Lang. {{ISBN|978-3-0343-2240-9}}

